column2: In Egyptian mythology, Ptah is created the world is the patron of craftsmanship, metalworking, carpentry, shipbuilding and sculpture. He is most popularly worshipped in Memphis.
Serve in the temple of Ptah
In our service to Ptah, we have to keep him fed and clean so that we will continue to be blessed by his grace. To perform this duty, we need help from the community...
To initiate this mission, activate the 'Serve in the temple' decision.
